<P>
China has set up a committee to select one school from every
province-level area as well as the five municipalities to
participate in the program.
</P>
<P>
Wang Yuqing, deputy director of the State Bureau of
Environmental Protection, attended the opening ceremony of the
workshop today. US Vice-President Al Gore sent a letter of
congratulations to the group.
</P>
<P>
Representatives from China's Ministry of Foreign Affairs, US
embassy in China and the Japanese embassy in Beijing also attended
the ceremony.
</P>
<P>
</P>
</TEXT>
