<HEADLINE> All Bills to Be Enacted by July 1: HKSAR Spokesman </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 23 (Xinhua) -- The Chief Executive's Office of
the Hong Kong Special Administrative Region (HKSAR) said today
that it will submit to the Provisional Legislative Council (PLC)
as soon as possible all bills that must be enacted before July 1.
</P>
