<HEADLINE> Uruguayan President Visits Shanghai </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Huang briefed the guest on Shanghai's economic construction and
achievements scored in its social development, and expressed the
hope to further enhance cooperation between Shanghai and Uruguay
in economic sector.
</P>
<P>
Sanguinetti said that Shanghai's achievement in economic
construction, especially in the development of the Pudong New
Area, draws worldwide attention, from which Uruguay can learn
something.
</P>
<P>
Sanguinetti is convinced that his visit will help strengthen
the cooperative ties between the two sides.
</P>
<P>
Sanuinetti arrived here from Beijing yesterday accompanied by
Hou Jie, Chairman of China's Government Reception Committee and
Minister of Construction.
</P>
<P>
During Sanuinetti's stay in Shanghai, He toured Jinqiao export
processing area in Pudong, Shanghai-Bell Telephone Equipment
Manufacturing Co.Ltd. and the oriental pearl television
tower. 
