<HEADLINE> Gold Price in Hong Kong Down </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
HONG KONG, April 23 (Xinhua) -- The gold price in Hong Kong
today fell 11 HK dollars to close at 3,153 HK dollars a tael,
according to Po Sang Bank, one of the major gold dealers in Hong
Kong.
</P>
<P>
The gold price is equivalent to 341.92 US dollars a troy ounce,
down 0.91 US dollars at today's exchange rate of one US dollar to
7.7405 HK dollars.  
</P>
