<BODY>
<HEADLINE> Chinese President Gives Speech at Russian Duma (Part V) </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Since the beginning of reform and opening-up 19 years ago,
China has witnessed spectacular economic expansion, marked
improvement in people's living standards, increased ethnic harmony
and a dynamic and vigorous national life. All this has been
achieved under the guidance of Deng Xiaoping's theory of building
socialism with Chinese characteristics. This theory is the single
most precious asset of the Chinese Communist Party and the Chinese
people. Though Comrade Deng is no longer with us, China's current
domestic and foreign policies will not change, nor is there any
such possibility. Because these policies were formulated in
accordance with China's national interests and the will of its
people. They suit to our national conditions, and have received
the wholehearted support of the Chinese people. We will carry
forward Comrade Deng Xiaoping's behest, and, holding high the
great banner of building socialism with Chinese characteristics,
advance steadily our cause of reform, opening-up and modernization.
</P>
<P>
In some 60 days, the Chinese Government will resume the
exercise of sovereignty over Hong Kong. This is a major step
towards the accomplishment of our grand cause of national
reunification. We will ensure Macao's smooth return and the final
settlement of the Taiwan question by continuing to follow "one
country, two systems" policy, for this represents the common
aspiration of the entire Chinese nation.
</P>
<P>
China can not develop itself in isolation of the rest of the
world and the world also needs China for its own development. The
maintenance of long-term social stability and economic prosperity
in China is crucial both to the country itself and to the world at
large. China will unswervingly keep to the road of development
suited to its national conditions while vigorously absorbing all
the achievements of human civilization. It stands ready to
conduct extensive international cooperation on the basis of
equality and mutual benefit so as to make ever greater
contributions to world peace and development.
</P>
<P>
With the dawn of a new century breaking on the horizon, we find
ourselves at an important historical moment. The Chinese people
are ready to work with the Russian people and the people in the
rest of the world towards the establishment of a just and
equitable new international order and the creation of a better
world for all.
</P>
<P>
Thank you!
</P>
</TEXT>
</BODY>
