6-7 to discuss means of contributing to the economic reform and
development projects in Egypt in the near future.
</P>
<P>
The meetings will tackle the latest economic developments in
Egypt and the outstanding achievements effected by structural
adjustment programs in addition to development priorities and
funding needs in this respect, Egypt's Minister of Economy and
