continent which are going to feature high on the agenda as well
as other relevant issues including the Zairean crisis," he said.
</P>
<P>
He said the situation was evolving fast and the organization's
position had been made clear in the past.
</P>
<P>
He said OAU was calling for negotiations through peaceful
means which will ensure a ceasefire allowing the people of Zaire
to decide their future by themselves. 
