help reduce the inflation rate and the unemployment rate, it
said. But the unemployment rate will drop by no more than 0.5
percent.
</P>
<P>
In 1997, the growth in private consumption will be lower than
the economic growth, and the price index in the third quarter of
the year is expected to fluctuate within 2 percent, it
said. 
