Commander-in-Chief of the Chilean navy, Admiral Jorge Martinez
Busch, the naval Chief-of-Staff, Rear Admiral Jorge Arancibia
Reyes, and the Commander-in-Chief of the first naval zone, Rear
Admiral German Godda.
