<HEADLINE> New Exhibition on Nanjing Massacre </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, April 23 (Xinhua) -- An exhibition is held yesterday
in Beijing to mark the 60th year of the Nanjing Massacre,
according to today's "China Daily".
</P>
<P>
