Goodwill Games president Michael Plant said that the
organisers were quite sure the world class athletes would take
part in the games at the top of their game.
</P>
<P>
"In order to build a credible event, we had to induce people
to come." said Plant.
</P>
<P>
Some 1,300 athletes from more than 70 countries and regions
are expected to compete in the games from July 19 to August 2.
</P>
